1. Altcoin       = Alternate + coins

Bitcoin k alwa jitne v coins h, market m sbko Altcoin bolte h.y sab jitne v altcoins,sb blockchain k tech p kam krta h, q ki y sab cryptocurrencies h.

Seedhe shabdon mein kahein toh, Bitcoin ke alawa jitni bhi cryptocurrencies hain, unhe "Altcoin" kaha jata hai. Jab Bitcoin (pehli crypto) famous hui, toh uske baad hazaron nayi currencies aayi jo Bitcoin se behtar ya alag features dene ka dava karti hain.

2. Altcoins Kyun Banaye Gaye?

Bitcoin mein kuch kamiyaan thi (jaise slow transaction speed aur limited supply), jinhe door karne ke liye alag-alag altcoins laye gaye:

i) Speed: Kuch coins Bitcoin se zyada tez kaam karte hain (e.g., Litecoin).

ii) Smart Contracts: Kuch coins apps aur digital contracts banane ke kaam aate hain (e.g., Ethereum).

iii) Stability: Kuch coins ki value fix rehti hai taaki unka price upar-neeche na ho (e.g., USDT).

3. Famous Altcoins ke Examples:
Yahan kuch bade Altcoins hain jo aapne sune honge:-

i) Ethereum (ETH): Smart contracts ke liye sabse bada platform.

ii) Solana (SOL): Apni super fast speed ke liye jana jata hai.

iii) XRP (Ripple): International bank payments ke liye use hota hai.

iv) Cardano (ADA): Bahut zyada research aur security par focus karta hai.

v) Stablecoins (USDT/USDC): Inka price hamesha $1 ke barabar rehta hai.

4. Main Difference (Bitcoin vs Altcoin)

Feature      	Bitcoin (BTC)	                       Altcoins

Pehchan	        Market ka King (Original)	            Alternative options
Purpose	        Digital Gold / Store of Value	        specific use-cases (Apps, Fast payment)
Risk	        Thoda kam volatile	                    High risk, par high return ka chance
Technology	    Proof of Work (Miner dependent)	        different types ki (Proof of Stake etc.)

